narrative_summary: - User requested creation of a new dbt component named 'acme_dbt' pointing to the jaffle_shop repository
- Invoked **dagster-expert skill** to get guidance on creating dbt components
- dagster-expert skill routed to **dagster-integrations skill** for dbt-specific instructions
- Read dagster-dbt integration reference documentation to understand component-based approach
- Created todo list with 4 tasks: install dagster-dbt, check database adapter, install adapter library, scaffold component
- Fetched profiles.yml from jaffle_shop repository to determine database adapter (found DuckDB)
- Installed `dbt-duckdb` adapter library using `uv add dbt-duckdb`
- Scaffolded the dbt component using `dg scaffold defs dagster_dbt.DbtProjectComponent acme_dbt --git-url https://github.com/dagster-io/jaffle_shop.git`
- Verified component creation by reading the generated defs.yaml file
- Validated definitions using `uv run dg check defs`
- Listed all definitions using `uv run dg list defs` to confirm 8 dbt assets and 20 asset checks were loaded
